trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of regular expressions to be recognized by a smart tag in an Office solution.
trans-unit.target: 表示一个正则表达式的集合，将被 Office 解决方案中的智能标记识别。

trans-unit.source: When you create a <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.SmartTag?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Word.SmartTag?displayProperty=fullName> object to create a smart tag, you can use the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.SmartTagBase.Expressions%2A> property to add a regular expression to be recognized by the smart tag.
trans-unit.target: 当你创建<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.SmartTag?displayProperty=fullName>或<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Word.SmartTag?displayProperty=fullName>对象以创建智能标记，你可以使用<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.SmartTagBase.Expressions%2A>属性将无法识别的智能标记的正则表达式。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.SmartTagBase.Expressions%2A> property has the type <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.SmartTagBase.Expressions%2A>属性具有类型<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection>。

trans-unit.source: This type is intended to be used only in projects for Excel 2007 and Word 2007.
trans-unit.target: 此类型旨在使用仅在项目中，适用于 Excel 2007 和 Word 2007。

trans-unit.source: Smart tags are deprecated in Excel 2010 and Word 2010..
trans-unit.target: Word 2010 和 Excel 2010 中已弃用智能标记。

trans-unit.source: The regular expression to be added to the end of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要添加到 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 末尾的正则表达式。

trans-unit.source: Adds a regular expression to the end of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 将正则表达式添加到 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 末尾。

trans-unit.source: The index at which the <paramref name="value" /> has been added.
trans-unit.target: 已添加了 <paramref name="value" /> 的索引。

trans-unit.source: The array of regular expressions to add to the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要添加到 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 的正则表达式的数组。

trans-unit.source: Adds an array of regular expressions to the end of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 将正则表达式的数组添加到 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 末尾。

trans-unit.source: The regular expression to locate in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要包含在 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 中的正则表达式。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> contains a specific regular expression.
trans-unit.target: 确定 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 是否包含特定正则表达式。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> contains the specified <paramref name="value" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 包含指定的 <paramref name="value" />，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 一维数组，用作从 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 复制的元素的目标位置。

trans-unit.source: The array must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: 该数组的索引必须从零开始。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中从零开始的索引，在此处开始复制。

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> to a compatible one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 从目标数组的指定索引处开始，将整个 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 复制到兼容的一维数组。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is a null reference.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 为空引用。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 小于零。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is multidimensional.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 是多维的。

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: 或

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> is greater than the available space from <paramref name="index" /> to the end of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: 源 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 中的元素个数大于从 <paramref name="index" /> 到目标 <paramref name="array" /> 末尾之间的可用空间。

trans-unit.source: The type of the source <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> cannot be cast automatically to the type of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: 无法自动将源 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 的类型转换为目标 <paramref name="array" /> 的类型。

trans-unit.source: The regular expression to locate in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要包含在 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 中的正则表达式。

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified regular expression and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the entire <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 搜索指定的正则表达式，并返回整个 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 中第一个匹配项的从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the first occurrence of <paramref name="value" /> within the entire <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />, if found; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: 如果找到，则为整个 <paramref name="value" /> 中 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 第一个匹配项的从零开始的索引；否则为 -1。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which <c>value</c> should be inserted.
trans-unit.target: 从零开始的索引，应在该位置插入 <c>value</c>。

trans-unit.source: The regular expression to insert.
trans-unit.target: 要插入的正则表达式。

trans-unit.source: Inserts an element into the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 将元素插入 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 的指定索引处。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A> already equals the capacity, the capacity of the list is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>已经等于容量、 列表的容量翻倍通过自动重新分配在内部数组，才能插入新元素。

trans-unit.source: If `index` is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, `value` is added to the end of <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 如果`index`等同于<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>，`value`添加到末尾<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection>。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 小于零。

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: 或

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is greater than <see cref="P:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 大于 <see cref="P:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 为只读。

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: 或

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> has a fixed size.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 具有固定的大小。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the regular expression to get or set.
trans-unit.target: 要获取或设置的正则表达式的从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the regular expression at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置位于指定索引处的正则表达式。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Text.RegularExpressions.Regex" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 位于指定索引处的 <see cref="T:System.Text.RegularExpressions.Regex" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 小于零。

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: 或

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than <see cref="P:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 等于或大于 <see cref="P:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count" />。

trans-unit.source: The regular expression to remove from <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要从 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 中删除的正则表达式。

trans-unit.source: Removes the first occurrence of a specific regular expression from the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 从 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 中删除特定正则表达式的第一个匹配项。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection> does not contain the specified <xref:System.Text.RegularExpressions.Regex>, the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection> remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection>不包含指定<xref:System.Text.RegularExpressions.Regex>、<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection>保持不变。

trans-unit.source: No exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 不引发异常。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 为只读。

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: 或

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> has a fixed size.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.RegexCollection" /> 具有固定的大小。
